      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>This small, smooth stone glows with a pale light that sheds dim light in a 20-foot radius around you. Once per day, you can spend 10 minutes focusing on the brenneri stone to gain an additional effect; this doesn&rsquo;t count as resting to regain Stamina Points. After you use the stone, the radius of its light effect is reduced to 5 feet for 24 hours. You can gain the benefits of only one brenneri stone per day. Brenneris can use their favored object racial trait with a brenneri stone and gain the benefits of both the item and the class feature.</p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Glossy:</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">You gain a +2 morale bonus against fear effects for 1 hour.</span></p>"
